{"pageProps":{"article":{"id":"5f75d955ad","title":"杜秉锐的痛快和不满","origin":"","is_range_date":false,"dates":[{"id":"25cbd6433a","index":0,"year":1957,"month":6,"day":20,"articleId":"5f75d955ad"}],"tags":[{"id":"c9f57d6426","name":"文章","type":"文稿类型"}],"aliases":[],"publications":[{"id":"CCRD-fanyou","name":"中国反右运动数据库","internal":false,"official":false,"type":"db","author":"宋永毅","files":""}],"authors":[{"id":"a6ebd070fa","name":"中国人民解放军"},{"id":"e1d73547cc","name":"杜秉锐"}]},"publication_details":{"CCRD-fanyou":{"comments":[],"contents":[{"id":"1f0c6791ba","type":"title","text":"杜秉锐的痛快和不满","index":0,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5f75d955ad"},{"id":"4d5e343192","type":"authors","text":"中国人民解放军杜秉锐","index":1,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5f75d955ad"},{"id":"5511434ff0","type":"paragraph","text":"海军航空兵翻译室杜秉锐在看到报纸上登载的葛佩琦的言论后，拍着桌子说：“痛快”，“说的对”！还说：“此人一定有冤枉，人民日报记者应当去访问他一下。”有人对他说：“你有意见就‘鸣’嘛！”杜秉锐说：“应当喊‘杀’！坏党员应当杀！”","index":2,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5f75d955ad"},{"id":"2fb5f2f131","type":"paragraph","text":"在这以后的一次座谈会上，杜秉锐又说：“现在看来，葛佩琦是孤立的了！没有人来支持他。现在是‘围剿’了！反党言论的大帽子太厉害了！”","index":3,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5f75d955ad"},{"id":"1188437bcf","type":"paragraph","text":"看到储安平的“党天下”的言论后，杜秉锐说：“任何人不能讲共产党的坏话，说坏话的就是坏人，唯唯诺诺是好人。”又说：“只要有党员的单位，党员总是头头。”","index":4,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5f75d955ad"},{"id":"7055ee33ba","type":"paragraph","text":" 来源：1957年6月20日《解放军报》。","index":5,"publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5f75d955ad"}],"page":{"id":"24595405cf","publicationId":"CCRD-fanyou","articleId":"5f75d955ad","start":0,"end":0}}}},"__N_SSG":true}